{"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":0,"metadata":{"colab":{"provenance":[],"authorship_tag":"ABX9TyNDzxg6M93NdeSuP3o8nTHx"},"kernelspec":{"name":"python3","display_name":"Python 3"},"language_info":{"name":"python"}},"cells":[{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##STRINGS\n","\n","Son el tipo de dato que incluye Textos. Cualquier informacion escrita como un texto es considerado como un \"String\"."],"metadata":{"id":"uR6DXiQUzv1t"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["text = 'Hola mundo' #Esto es un String"],"metadata":{"id":"JHPtnAsR0eSV"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["También podemos crear strings multimedias haciendo uso de tres comillas simples (''') o tres pares de comillas dobles (\"\"\")."],"metadata":{"id":"p3NbAE-B1x2a"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##SECUENCIAS DE ESCAPE\n","\n","* \\n Linea Nueva\n","* \\t Tabulacion (8 espacios)\n","* \\n Back slash\n","* ': Single quote(')\n","* \": Double quote(\")"],"metadata":{"id":"sRw-0wmJ2ZMl"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["print('Este es un ejemplo de salto de linea. \\n¿Lo notas?') # line break\n","print('Dia\\tTemas\\tEjercicios') # Agregado una tabulacion\n","print('Dia 1\\t3\\t5')"],"metadata":{"id":"ZL_LT-0B2mF0"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##STRINGS CON VARIABLES"],"metadata":{"id":"GErrSUfOoDds"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["name, surname, alias, age = 'Abdiel', 'Hernández', 'Teakosprey', 19\n","\n","print('Me llamo: ', name , surname)\n","print('Mi edad es: ', age , 'Mis amigos me dicen: ', alias)"],"metadata":{"id":"0fjZ8M-ioRLs"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["print('Mi nombre es {} {} y mi edad es {}', format(name, surname, age))\n","print('Mi nombre es %s %s y mi edad es %d' %(name, surname, age))\n","print(f'Mi nombre es {name} {surname} y mi edad es {age}')               #Esta es la mejor forma de hacerlo."],"metadata":{"id":"71_CIRXro5Ey"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##STRINGS COMO SECUENCIA DE CARACTERES\n","\n","Los strings son secuencias de letras unidas que forman palabras. Tenemos distintas maneras de descomponer un string en cada una de las unidades, sin embargo la manera más simple de extraer cada miembro de un string es desempaquetarlo en distintas variables."],"metadata":{"id":"0-mjQFRZp_kA"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["lenguaje = 'PYTHON'\n","a, b, c, d, e, f = lenguaje\n","print(a)\n","print(b)\n","print(c)\n","print(d)\n","print(e)\n","print(f)"],"metadata":{"id":"0Bgb5OcGp0cf"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["lenguaje = 123456\n","print(type(lenguaje))\n","lenguaje = str(lenguaje)\n","print(type(lenguaje))\n","a, b, c, d, e, f = lenguaje\n","print(a)\n","print(b)\n","print(c)\n","print(d)\n","print(e)\n","print(f)\n","lenguaje = int(lenguaje)\n","print(type(lenguaje))"],"metadata":{"id":"pf1fy0xfrV45"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["primer_letra = lenguaje [0]\n","segunda_letra = lenguaje [1]\n","tercer_letra = lenguaje [2]\n","print(primer_letra)\n","print(segunda_letra)\n","print(tercer_letra)"],"metadata":{"id":"aZJGXsTSsDns"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##RECORTANDO STRINGS"],"metadata":{"id":"WwulEQHotZNb"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["lenguaje = 'PYTHON'\n","primeros_tres = lenguaje [0:3] #inicia en cero y sube hasta llegar a 3, pero NO incluye el 3.\n","print(primeros_tres)           #Muestra las primeras tres letras (PYT)\n","\n","ultimos_tres = lenguaje [3:6]  #inicia en 3 pero inclue el 3, y sube hasta llegar a 6 aunque solo necesitamos que llegue al 5.\n","print(ultimos_tres)            #Muestra las últimas tres letras (HON).\n","\n","#Otra forma (PYTHON)\n","ultimos_tres = lenguaje[-3:]\n","print(ultimos_tres)            #HOM\n","primeros_tres = lenguaje [:-3]\n","print(primeros_tres)           #PYT"],"metadata":{"id":"Nq0Pz7NDtb3N"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##INVIRTIENDO STRINGS"],"metadata":{"id":"_jLBCBrZv5TJ"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["saludo = 'Hello, World'\n","print(saludo[::-1])"],"metadata":{"id":"JHeUNSiQv74w"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##SALTANDO LETRAS"],"metadata":{"id":"sUVpZmrqwIfx"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["lenguaje = 'PYTHON'\n","new = lenguaje[0:6:2]\n","print(new)"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"VP0QaGLPwLJT","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1675284861548,"user_tz":360,"elapsed":178,"user":{"displayName":"Teakosprey","userId":"04041112761850926622"}},"outputId":"48d13a47-45ff-451e-eb21-350eef0b6fbf"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["PTO\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##**MÉTODOS CON STRINGS**"],"metadata":{"id":"T6dDpkSvwpg4"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##CONVERTIR LA PRIMERA LETRA EN MAYÚSCULA"],"metadata":{"id":"5isCJUejw2PO"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["text = 'aprendiendo python en clase'\n","print(text.capitalize())"],"metadata":{"id":"KsUZ9jgRxnJN"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["text = 'aprendiendo' + 'Python' + 'en clase'\n","print(type(text))\n","text = 'aprendiendo python en clase'\n","print(type(text))\n","print(text.capitalize())"],"metadata":{"id":"nFoUq6Ktw9xh"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##CONTAR LAS VECES QUE SE REPITE UN CARACTER"],"metadata":{"id":"TIL0QKvdxtx7"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["text = 'aprendiendo python en clase'\n","print(text.count('a'))               #Va a buscar cuantas veces está la letra \"a\" en toda la oración.\n","print(text.count('y', 7, 14))        #Va a buscar cuantas veces está la letra \"y\" en en un rango de 7 a 14 caracteres.\n","print(text.count('en'))              #Va a buscar cuantas veces está la palabra \"en\" en toda la oración. "],"metadata":{"id":"0z593UbKxy6y"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##REGRESA LA POSICIÓN DONDE SE ENCUENTRA EL CARACTER\n","\n","Si no se encuentra regresa -1."],"metadata":{"id":"POfhrUG5yspj"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":["text = 'aprendiendo python en clase'\n","print(text.find('y'))\n","print(text.find('th'))\n","print(text.find('am'))"],"metadata":{"id":"7JYy-wmJzEt3"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["##**ACTIVIDAD**\n","\n","Genera palíndromos y comprueba que efectivamente lo son"],"metadata":{"id":"NNzQR85qs3oj"}},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":null,"metadata":{"id":"VlqHm0eGk-PU"},"outputs":[],"source":["palabra = (input(\"Ingrese una palabra Palíndroma: \"))\n","print(palabra[::-1])"]}]}